{
  "title": "The best new Android apps and games for December 2024",
  "content": "<div><main class=\"d_3 d_o\"><div class=\"d_d\"><div class=\"d_Ed d_B\"><div class=\"d_Dd\"><div class=\"d_f\"><div class=\"d_nr\"><picture class=\"d_Lg\"><source sizes=\"(min-width: 64rem) 51.25rem, 80vw\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-icon-1.jpg.webp 1920w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-icon-1-1536w-864h.jpg.webp 1536w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-icon-1-675w-380h.jpg.webp 675w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-icon-1-64w-36h.jpg.webp 64w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-icon-1-1000w-563h.jpg.webp 1000w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-icon-1-300w-170h.jpg.webp 300w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-icon-1-1280w-720h.jpg.webp 1280w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-icon-1-840w-472h.jpg.webp 840w\" type=\"image/webp\"><img class=\"d_Mg\" sizes=\"(min-width: 64rem) 51.25rem, 80vw\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-icon-1.jpg 1920w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-icon-1-1536w-864h.jpg 1536w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-icon-1-675w-380h.jpg 675w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-icon-1-64w-36h.jpg 64w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-icon-1-1000w-563h.jpg 1000w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-icon-1-300w-170h.jpg 300w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-icon-1-1280w-720h.jpg 1280w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-icon-1-840w-472h.jpg 840w\" alt=\"clean as duck icon 1\" src=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-icon-1.jpg\"></picture></div></div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><p>Many new Android apps are out there. Keeping track of them is tough, but we’re happy to do that hard work for you. We’ve scoured the internet to find the best new Android apps and new Android games available, focusing on titles that offer something different to the status quo. Be sure to visit our list of the <a href=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/best-android-apps-312570/\">best Android apps</a> of all time, the <a href=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/best-android-games-316202/\">best Android games</a> ever, and our selection of the <a href=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/best-apps-released-2023-3399892/\">best new Android apps released in 2023</a> for more.</p>\n</div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><h2 class=\"\">The best new Android apps and games for December 2024</h2>\n<ol class=\"\">\n<li><a href=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/new-android-apps-658839/#1\">Aggregator RSS</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/new-android-apps-658839/#2\">Clean As Duck</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/new-android-apps-658839/#3\">TED Tumblewords</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/new-android-apps-658839/#4\">Snaky Cat</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/new-android-apps-658839/#5\">PixelShot</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/new-android-apps-658839/#6\">Carrion</a></li>\n</ol>\n</div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><h2 id=\"1\" class=\"\">Aggregator RSS</h2>\n<p><strong>An RSS aggregator with a dizzying number of sources and a clean UI.<br>\n</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Price: </strong>Free</li>\n<li><strong>Developer:</strong> AndreaA</li>\n</ul>\n</div><div class=\"d_kk d_e\"><button type=\"button\"><picture class=\"d_Lg\"><source sizes=\"calc(min(calc(100vw - 1.875rem), 51.25rem) / 3)\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-002.jpg.webp 498w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-002-398w-864h.jpg.webp 398w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-002-175w-380h.jpg.webp 175w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-002-30w-64h.jpg.webp 30w\" type=\"image/webp\"><img class=\"d_Mg\" sizes=\"calc(min(calc(100vw - 1.875rem), 51.25rem) / 3)\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-002.jpg 498w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-002-398w-864h.jpg 398w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-002-175w-380h.jpg 175w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-002-30w-64h.jpg 30w\" alt=\"aggregator rss android app screens 002\" src=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-002.jpg\"></picture></button><button type=\"button\"><picture class=\"d_Lg\"><source sizes=\"calc(min(calc(100vw - 1.875rem), 51.25rem) / 3)\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-003.jpg.webp 498w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-003-398w-864h.jpg.webp 398w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-003-175w-380h.jpg.webp 175w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-003-30w-64h.jpg.webp 30w\" type=\"image/webp\"><img class=\"d_Mg\" sizes=\"calc(min(calc(100vw - 1.875rem), 51.25rem) / 3)\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-003.jpg 498w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-003-398w-864h.jpg 398w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-003-175w-380h.jpg 175w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-003-30w-64h.jpg 30w\" alt=\"aggregator rss android app screens 003\" src=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-003.jpg\"></picture></button><button type=\"button\"><picture class=\"d_Lg\"><source sizes=\"calc(min(calc(100vw - 1.875rem), 51.25rem) / 3)\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-001.jpg.webp 498w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-001-398w-864h.jpg.webp 398w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-001-175w-380h.jpg.webp 175w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-001-30w-64h.jpg.webp 30w\" type=\"image/webp\"><img class=\"d_Mg\" sizes=\"calc(min(calc(100vw - 1.875rem), 51.25rem) / 3)\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-001.jpg 498w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-001-398w-864h.jpg 398w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-001-175w-380h.jpg 175w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-001-30w-64h.jpg 30w\" alt=\"aggregator rss android app screens 001\" src=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aggregator-rss-android-app-screens-001.jpg\"></picture></button></div><div class=\"d_e d_C\">\n<p>Aggregator RSS flew under the radar this year. After my toils trying to find a reliable <a href=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/google-news-alternative-3487186/\">Google News alternative</a>, I missed this absolute gem of an app hiding in plain sight.</p></div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><p>The app is true to its name, offering users easy access to various news sources categorized by topic or industry. Once you’ve selected which to follow, the app presents a rolling feed of news items from its preloaded source lists. You can tinker with these, removing or adding your own sites. A read later feature helps you stow articles away for safekeeping.</p></div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><p>I will say that Aggregator still feels like a relatively young app. It lacks an internal reader — a big shame considering its many sources — and the inability to easily remove a site from an article is another odd exclusion. That said, I’m nitpicking. The app is clean, swift, and free. If anything, it’s useful for discovering sources you enjoy reading.</p>\n</div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><h2 id=\"2\" class=\"\">Clean As Duck</h2>\n<p><strong>This app will soothe your hate for household chores.<br>\n</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Price: </strong>Free</li>\n<li><strong>Developer:</strong> wilmo</li>\n</ul>\n</div><div class=\"d_kk d_e\"><button type=\"button\"><picture class=\"d_Lg\"><source sizes=\"calc(min(calc(100vw - 1.875rem), 51.25rem) / 3)\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-008.jpg.webp 498w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-008-398w-864h.jpg.webp 398w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-008-175w-380h.jpg.webp 175w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-008-30w-64h.jpg.webp 30w\" type=\"image/webp\"><img class=\"d_Mg\" sizes=\"calc(min(calc(100vw - 1.875rem), 51.25rem) / 3)\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-008.jpg 498w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-008-398w-864h.jpg 398w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-008-175w-380h.jpg 175w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-008-30w-64h.jpg 30w\" alt=\"clean as duck google tasks alternative chores 008\" src=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-008.jpg\"></picture></button><button type=\"button\"><picture class=\"d_Lg\"><source sizes=\"calc(min(calc(100vw - 1.875rem), 51.25rem) / 3)\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-002.jpg.webp 498w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-002-398w-864h.jpg.webp 398w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-002-175w-380h.jpg.webp 175w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-002-30w-64h.jpg.webp 30w\" type=\"image/webp\"><img class=\"d_Mg\" sizes=\"calc(min(calc(100vw - 1.875rem), 51.25rem) / 3)\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-002.jpg 498w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-002-398w-864h.jpg 398w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-002-175w-380h.jpg 175w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-002-30w-64h.jpg 30w\" alt=\"clean as duck google tasks alternative chores 002\" src=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-002.jpg\"></picture></button><button type=\"button\"><picture class=\"d_Lg\"><source sizes=\"calc(min(calc(100vw - 1.875rem), 51.25rem) / 3)\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-005.jpg.webp 498w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-005-398w-864h.jpg.webp 398w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-005-175w-380h.jpg.webp 175w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-005-30w-64h.jpg.webp 30w\" type=\"image/webp\"><img class=\"d_Mg\" sizes=\"calc(min(calc(100vw - 1.875rem), 51.25rem) / 3)\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-005.jpg 498w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-005-398w-864h.jpg 398w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-005-175w-380h.jpg 175w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-005-30w-64h.jpg 30w\" alt=\"clean as duck google tasks alternative chores 005\" src=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/clean-as-duck-google-tasks-alternative-chores-005.jpg\"></picture></button></div><div class=\"d_e d_C\">\n<p>Some people like chores, others hate them. Personally, I revel in them. I can’t start my day until I’ve checked all the boxes on my morning household tasks list. However, some chores that don’t require daily address are often forgotten. That’s where I’ve found <a href=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/google-tasks-alternative-chores-3501415/\">Clean As Duck</a> to be immensely helpful.</p></div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><p>The app focuses on helping you collate, manage, and complete tasks that you may overlook otherwise. It’s stocked with several templates for daily, weekly, or less frequent recurring tasks that you can add to your personal to-do list. Have you remembered to clean your fridge’s coils, dust the radiator, or clean your windows? Clean As Duck will remind you (that you actually need to be doing these things).</p></div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><p>While you could use a traditional to-do list app for chores or something like <a href=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/how-i-use-obsidian-3499300/\">Obsidian</a>, I’ve found a dedicated solution to minimize distractions. Clean As Duck’s purpose-built bones are perfect in this sense.</p>\n</div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><h2 id=\"3\" class=\"\">TED Tumblewords</h2>\n<p><strong>A tile-sliding, word-forming, quick-thinking game from TED and Netflix.<br>\n</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Price: </strong>Free / Requires an active Netflix subscription</li>\n<li><strong>Developer:</strong> Frosty Pop / Netflix</li>\n</ul>\n</div><div class=\"d_e d_C\">\n<p>Netflix has quite a mobile games library, and this latest addition will likely appeal to Wordle players who want a new challenge.</p></div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><p>In short, TED Tumblewords is a tile-sliding game that encourages players to form word chains by unscrambling the letters presented. It’s a strange combination of Scrabble and Countdown’s word game but oddly addictive. Players can choose from many topics and play against others. The game also includes a ranking system and collectible cards.</p></div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><p>Notably, unlike Wordle, Tumblewords’s gameplay is rapid, but daily challenges make it worth dropping in daily. I’m not sure if this title will stay on my frequently played list for a long time, though.</p></div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><p>Unfortunately, as it’s a Netflix-published game, you will need a <a href=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/netflix-standard-vs-premium-3282785/\">Netflix subscription</a> to play it, but it’s well worth a go if you do.</p>\n</div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><h2 id=\"4\" class=\"\">Snaky Cat</h2>\n<p><strong>Think Snake, but with cats and donuts and much better graphics.<br>\n</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Price: </strong>Free / In-app purchases</li>\n<li><strong>Developer:</strong> Appxplore</li>\n</ul></div><div class=\"d_f\"><div class=\"d_nr\"><picture class=\"d_Lg\"><source sizes=\"(min-width: 64rem) 51.25rem, 80vw\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snaky-cat-android-game.jpg.webp 1920w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snaky-cat-android-game-1536w-864h.jpg.webp 1536w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snaky-cat-android-game-675w-380h.jpg.webp 675w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snaky-cat-android-game-64w-36h.jpg.webp 64w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snaky-cat-android-game-1000w-563h.jpg.webp 1000w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snaky-cat-android-game-300w-170h.jpg.webp 300w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snaky-cat-android-game-1280w-720h.jpg.webp 1280w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snaky-cat-android-game-840w-472h.jpg.webp 840w\" type=\"image/webp\"><img class=\"d_Mg\" sizes=\"(min-width: 64rem) 51.25rem, 80vw\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snaky-cat-android-game.jpg 1920w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snaky-cat-android-game-1536w-864h.jpg 1536w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snaky-cat-android-game-675w-380h.jpg 675w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snaky-cat-android-game-64w-36h.jpg 64w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snaky-cat-android-game-1000w-563h.jpg 1000w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snaky-cat-android-game-300w-170h.jpg 300w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snaky-cat-android-game-1280w-720h.jpg 1280w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snaky-cat-android-game-840w-472h.jpg 840w\" alt=\"snaky cat android game\" src=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snaky-cat-android-game.jpg\"></picture></div></div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><p>I have a Nokia 3310 lying in a box somewhere, and I’d love nothing more than to get it up and running again so I can play a few rounds of Snake. But I guess Snaky Cat will suffice for now.</p></div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><p>This modern take on the classic title sees you playing as a particularly ravenous cat which grows ever longer the more donuts it consumes. The game also has a multiplayer element, but you’ll want to stay well away from them lest you become a pile of pastries yourself.</p></div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><p>The gameplay is surprisingly slow, but that’s to its advantage. A scale-down skill tree element also allows you to increase speed effects and multipliers. And unlike Snake, Snaky Cat’s gameplay is split into timed rounds. I feel this somewhat breaks the game’s momentum but does lessen the chance of giant cat griefers bullying smaller kittens just getting started.</p>\n</div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><h2 id=\"5\" class=\"\">PixelShot</h2>\n<p><strong>Pixel Screenshots for the Android masses brought by a third-party developer.<br>\n</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Price: </strong>Free</li>\n<li><strong>Developer:</strong> Aculix Technologies LLP</li>\n</ul>\n</div><div class=\"d_kk d_e\"><button type=\"button\"><picture class=\"d_Lg\"><source sizes=\"calc(min(calc(100vw - 1.875rem), 51.25rem) / 3)\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_1.png.webp 898w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_1-674w-1440h.png.webp 674w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_1-505w-1080h.png.webp 505w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_1-404w-864h.png.webp 404w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_1-178w-380h.png.webp 178w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_1-30w-64h.png.webp 30w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_1-562w-1200h.png.webp 562w\" type=\"image/webp\"><img class=\"d_Mg\" sizes=\"calc(min(calc(100vw - 1.875rem), 51.25rem) / 3)\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_1.png 898w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_1-674w-1440h.png 674w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_1-505w-1080h.png 505w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_1-404w-864h.png 404w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_1-178w-380h.png 178w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_1-30w-64h.png 30w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_1-562w-1200h.png 562w\" alt=\"PixelShot screenshot view 1\" src=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_1.png\"></picture></button><button type=\"button\"><picture class=\"d_Lg\"><source sizes=\"calc(min(calc(100vw - 1.875rem), 51.25rem) / 3)\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_2.png.webp 898w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_2-674w-1440h.png.webp 674w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_2-505w-1080h.png.webp 505w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_2-404w-864h.png.webp 404w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_2-178w-380h.png.webp 178w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_2-30w-64h.png.webp 30w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_2-562w-1200h.png.webp 562w\" type=\"image/webp\"><img class=\"d_Mg\" sizes=\"calc(min(calc(100vw - 1.875rem), 51.25rem) / 3)\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_2.png 898w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_2-674w-1440h.png 674w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_2-505w-1080h.png 505w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_2-404w-864h.png 404w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_2-178w-380h.png 178w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_2-30w-64h.png 30w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_2-562w-1200h.png 562w\" alt=\"PixelShot screenshot view 2\" src=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_screenshot_view_2.png\"></picture></button><button type=\"button\"><picture class=\"d_Lg\"><source sizes=\"calc(min(calc(100vw - 1.875rem), 51.25rem) / 3)\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_home_page.png.webp 898w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_home_page-674w-1440h.png.webp 674w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_home_page-505w-1080h.png.webp 505w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_home_page-404w-864h.png.webp 404w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_home_page-178w-380h.png.webp 178w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_home_page-30w-64h.png.webp 30w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_home_page-562w-1200h.png.webp 562w\" type=\"image/webp\"><img class=\"d_Mg\" sizes=\"calc(min(calc(100vw - 1.875rem), 51.25rem) / 3)\" srcset=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_home_page.png 898w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_home_page-674w-1440h.png 674w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_home_page-505w-1080h.png 505w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_home_page-404w-864h.png 404w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_home_page-178w-380h.png 178w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_home_page-30w-64h.png 30w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_home_page-562w-1200h.png 562w\" alt=\"PixelShot home page\" src=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PixelShot_home_page.png\"></picture></button></div><div class=\"d_e d_C\">\n<p>Pixel smartphones get some <a href=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/best-pixel-features-explained-3217987/\">great exclusive features</a>, and one of the more intriguing to land in recent months is Pixel Screenshots. It effectively turns the humble screenshotting feature into an AI-fueled database of your snips. PixelShot is a third-party app that brings a similar feature to other Android smartphones.</p></div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><p>PixelShot stores and processes your screenshots, extracting any text from them and allowing users to search through them based on this information. It’s important to note that while most of the processing occurs on the device, some data is uploaded to the cloud. If you have personal information in your screenshots, it’s best to think twice about using it.</p>\n</div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><h2 id=\"6\" class=\"\">Carrion</h2>\n<p><strong>Who says December is too late for spooky horror games?<br>\n</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Price: </strong>Free / In-app purchases</li>\n<li><strong>Developer:</strong> DevolverDigital</li>\n</ul>\n</div><div class=\"d_e d_C\">\n<p>Finally, here’s an app I’ve been playing for a few weeks now in between Pokemon TCG Pocket binge sessions. Perhaps it’s not a good fit for Holly Jolly December, but it is hugely cathartic when the holiday season gets a little stressful.</p></div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><p>You play as a massive monster blob trapped in a facility. You aim to eat as many minions as possible, wreaking havoc in your wake and growing ever larger. The mechanics are incredibly simple, and you’ll get used to the controls after a few minutes. The tight and twisty map adds to the charm, too.</p></div><div class=\"d_e d_C\"><p>Carrion is free to try, but you’ll need to purchase an unlock to access all the horror on offer. Happy Holidays!</p>\n</div><div class=\"d_mc d_x\"></div></div><aside class=\"d_Cd\"></aside></div></div></main></div>",
